Package: edgebundleR
Type: Package
Title: Circle plot with bundled edges
Version: 0.0.3
Date: 2015-04-02
Authors@R: c(person("Garth", "Tarr", email = "garth.tarr@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
              person("Ellis", "Patrick", email = "ellis.patrick@sydney.edu.au", role = "aut"))
Description: Takes an appropriately structured JSON file or a square symmetric matrix (e.g. a
              correlation matrix or precision matrix) and outputs a circle plot with the nodes
              around the circumfrence and linkages between the connected nodes. Adapted from
              the  Mike Bostock's D3 Hierarchical Edge Bundling example using the htmlwidgets
              framework.
License: GPL (>= 2)
LazyData: TRUE
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.2),
    shiny
Imports:
    htmlwidgets,
    rjson,
    igraph
Suggests:
    knitr,
    htmltools (>= 0.2.6),
    huge
URL: https://github.com/garthtarr/edgebundleR
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Roxygen: list(wrap = FALSE)
